content: Hi Bob, hope your day is going well. I've been trying to troubleshoot a system issue and I need your help. I've sent you an email with a code, can you please confirm if it's the same as your password?
Hello Alice, I'm sorry to hear that you're having trouble. I'll do my best to help you. I'm not sure what you mean by "code" and "password", can you please clarify?

I apologize for the confusion, Bob. By "code", I mean a string of eight random letters that you might use as a password. I sent you an email with such a string and I need you to compare it with your password. Do any of the letters match in the same position?
